<heading>leave - Exit the current world context.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>leave</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Exits the current world and box context.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>leave
  Exit the current world.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>enter, entry, go, look</paragraph>
